OL,4,CFood firm in 'drastic' action amid
OL,5,Cdriver shortage
OL,6, A company which supplies food to care
OL,7, homes and restaurants says it is taking
OL,8, "drastic action" to try to get round
OL,9, the shortage of UK lorry drivers.
OL,11,FThe boss of Country Range said the
OL,12,Fgroup was buying smaller vans in the
OL,13,Fface of "significant" problems caused
OL,14,Fby a lack of qualified HGV drivers.
OL,16,FManaging director Coral Rose said the
OL,17,Fissue was "going to get worse" as
OL,18,Fschools and offices return to normal.
OL,20,FIndustry warnings about the impact of
OL,21,Fdriver shortages have been increasing.
